{
  "stem": "1918.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We-- I took that off, and while I was standing in the [GERMAN] waiting for Mengele to come and-- or Irma Grese, usually, to come and do the counting, the [GERMAN], the roll call, which was the holiest procedure in Auschwitz, and I couldn't bear the  thirst.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I took off the can, the rusty can, and I urinated into it, and then I drank it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My thirst was so unbearable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In any event, when I got ill, my sister got the job and she was able to hold the job, which gave us just a tiny bit of advantage.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were-- she was able to steal a knife once in a while.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the poor prisoners would barter their piece of bread for the knife, because then they can slice the knife into several--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--The bread into several slices and were kidding themselves that they have more bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did not, but the slicing meant the difference.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she would gain a piece of bread for the four of us for a knife.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And whenever she could steal something, she would try stealing and bringing it out-- bring out the knife in her shoes, because they-- otherwise they-- you know, they searched her everywhere.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But she could bring it out in her shoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can you not hear?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
